1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 10=

4
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:53,680
This place

5
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,520
is the old cultural center in Aiye Town.

6
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,000
Recently,

7
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:05,280
haven't you been worried
about the exhibition?

8
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,520
I brought you here to
pick out some paintings

9
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,400
that could be displayed
at the exhibition.

10
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:11,200
It'll help you relax a little too.

11
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,160
I feel like...

12
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,520
I've been here before.

13
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:22,440
Xiaomi.

14
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:23,800
Xiaomi.

15
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,880
This is where you used to study art.

16
00:01:33,689 --> 00:01:36,255
(Morning Light)

17
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,360
I have absolutely no inspiration.

18
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,920
Xiaomi.

19
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,560
If you're tired, let's just go home.

20
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,400
You can paint tomorrow.

21
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,120
Tomorrow?

22
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,600
The Orange Light Cup is
the day after tomorrow.

23
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,400
This time, I have to take first place.

24
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,400
So, what are you

25
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,040
planning to paint?

26
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,720
Can you go easy on me?

27
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,200
Maybe don't paint so well?

28
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,200
How am I

29
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,640
supposed to do that?

30
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,480
Xiaomi, if you want to win,

31
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,760
you have to rely on your own skills.

32
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,920
Dummy.

33
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,520
You really don't get it.

34
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,200
If I don't win first place, my dad...

35
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,600
So what are you planning to paint?

36
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,600
I...

37
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,280
I haven't decided yet.

38
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,320
No way.

39
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:43,840
Really.

40
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,280
Come on, tell me.

41
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,560
Did you hide it from me?

42
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,040
Tell me.

43
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:50,960
I really haven't.

44
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,560
Please tell me.

45
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,880
I'm begging you.

46
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,840
What's going on?

47
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,080
I'm scared.

48
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,600
What's happening?

49
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,880
Don't be scared.

50
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,760
It's probably just a power outage.

51
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,200
Then turn it back on!

52
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,840
Hurry up, you dummy!

53
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,400
Well...

54
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,760
Look.

55
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,320
Got any inspiration now?

56
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,440
Just tell me!

57
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,800
See that beam of light on the canvas?

58
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,120
Doesn't it look like
hope in the darkness?

59
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,360
A sunrise.

60
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,480
Morning Light.

61
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:54,560
You're incredible, Qin Yu.

62
00:03:57,991 --> 00:04:02,200
(Title: Morning Light;
Artist: Qiao Xiaomi)

63
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,880
Are you okay?

64
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,440
But...

65
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,440
did I really paint this?

66
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,400
Of course you did.

67
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,480
But...

68
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,000
you didn't paint it alone.

69
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,520
Otherwise, how do you think
you got that gold award?

70
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,200
You mean...

71
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,720
this painting...

72
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,000
was painted by both of us?

73
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:05,840
Right?

74
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,240
Then hurry up and tell me.

75
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,080
It doesn't matter anymore.

76
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,280
Maybe fate saw how
hard you worked before.

77
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,280
So it erased that memory on purpose.

78
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,880
Just to let you take it easy for once.

79
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,320
I guess you're right.

80
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,680
Out with the old, in with the new.

81
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,640
At worst,

82
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,560
I'll just switch careers.

83
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,280
Switch careers?

84
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,240
What are you going to do?

85
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,640
Bread.

86
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,160
From now on, I'll set up a stand here.

87
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,760
I've even thought of the name.

88
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,720
It'll be called...

89
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,600
Sweet Memories Lost.

90
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,560
Anyone who tells me a story

91
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,720
gets free bread.

92
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,600
I want to live in the present.

93
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,120
From now on, I'll open
a stall right here.

94
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,400
And help people get better.

95
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,840
If the elderly can't afford it,

96
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,040
I won't charge them a penny.

97
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,320
(Why is it that they look
completely different,)

98
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,160
(yet feel so alike?)

99
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,080
Why do I feel

100
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,920
like I've been here before too?

101
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,040
It feels like someone held my hand

102
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,960
and walked here with me.

103
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,360
Like this?

104
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,640
(How does she know that too?)

105
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,360
Thank you for bringing me here.

106
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:51,400
Compared to that cold,
busy city of Mancheng,

107
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,040
I like this place much more.

108
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,240
What do you like about it?

109
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,160
Its atmosphere. The
feeling of real life.

110
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,240
It's peaceful.

111
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,040
It's comfortable.

112
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,240
It makes you feel at ease.

113
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,280
After we graduate from college,

114
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,440
will you come back here?

115
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,560
Of course.

116
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,280
I like it here.

117
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,960
I like its atmosphere.

118
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,400
What atmosphere?

119
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,720
The feeling of real life.

120
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,720
Besides painting at the
old cultural center,

121
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,760
do we have

122
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,400
any other special memories here?

123
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,920
Back then,

124
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,800
that used to be a
traditional herbal clinic.

125
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,120
Now it's a convenience store.

126
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,200
The accident...

127
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,120
happened there that year.

128
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,640
Don't you remember?

129
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,440
Is anyone there?

130
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:06,080
Hello? Anyone?

131
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,600
Thank you for today.

132
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,320
I had a great time.

133
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,920
(I brought her to Aiye Town.)

134
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,120
(She was really happy today.)

135
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,840
(It's as if she's forgotten)

136
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,560
(what happened here.)

137
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,720
(She seems different.)

138
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,800
(Different from the Qiao Xiaomi
I used to know.)

139
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,960
(But for some reason,)

140
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,000
(sometimes I feel)

141
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,880
(that this difference)

142
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,120
(is strangely familiar.)

143
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,400
(I'm even starting to be drawn to her.)

144
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,400
(I really don't think)

145
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,040
(I can hate the Qiao Xiaomi
standing before me.)

146
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,160
(Should I keep doing this?)

147
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,640
You're drinking alone
without inviting me?

148
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,120
I didn't want to disturb your rest.

149
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,240
Qin Yu.

150
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,680
No.

151
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,280
Ji Ran.

152
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,240
Forget it.

153
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,120
A name isn't important.

154
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,000
It's just a name.

155
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,040
Qin Yu.

156
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,280
I've made a decision.

157
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,840
About what?

158
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,480
I've decided to stop dwelling on

159
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,680
getting my memories back.

160
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,080
I want to live in the present.

161
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,280
That's how people

162
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,480
should live, in the present.

163
00:11:36,795 --> 00:11:38,865
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

164
00:11:38,865 --> 00:11:42,285
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

165
00:11:43,885 --> 00:11:45,775
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

166
00:11:45,775 --> 00:11:49,765
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

167
00:11:51,005 --> 00:11:52,865
♪Let me go, set me free♪

168
00:11:52,865 --> 00:11:56,905
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

169
00:11:57,445 --> 00:12:02,855
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

170
00:12:04,205 --> 00:12:06,345
♪The freedom you gave me♪

171
00:12:06,345 --> 00:12:09,985
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

172
00:12:11,245 --> 00:12:13,515
♪Love can barely move forward♪

173
00:12:13,515 --> 00:12:17,295
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

174
00:12:18,395 --> 00:12:20,635
♪The closeness I long for♪

175
00:12:20,635 --> 00:12:25,025
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

176
00:12:25,435 --> 00:12:27,255
♪I don't want to break free♪

177
00:12:27,255 --> 00:12:32,625
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

